@BrowserAPI_HostAddress = http://localhost:5096

### 1. 获取浏览器服务配置
GET {{BrowserAPI_HostAddress}}/api/Browser/Options
Accept: application/json

### 2. 导航到 Bing
POST {{BrowserAPI_HostAddress}}/api/Browser/Navigate
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "url": "https://cn.bing.com/"
}

### 3. 获取页面 Arian 快照（扁平化）
GET {{BrowserAPI_HostAddress}}/api/Browser/Arian?flatten=true&interestingOnly=true
Accept: application/json

### 4. 获取页面 Arian 快照（树形结构）
GET {{BrowserAPI_HostAddress}}/api/Browser/Arian?flatten=false&interestingOnly=true
Accept: application/json

### 5. 在搜索框输入文本
POST {{BrowserAPI_HostAddress}}/api/Browser/Type
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "role": "searchbox",
  "name": "搜索",
  "text": "Browser Automation Test",
  "clearFirst": true,
  "timeoutMs": 5000
}

### 6. 按下回车键执行搜索
POST {{BrowserAPI_HostAddress}}/api/Browser/PressEnter
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "role": "searchbox",
  "name": "搜索",
  "timeoutMs": 5000
}

### 7. 等待 2 秒让页面加载
POST {{BrowserAPI_HostAddress}}/api/Browser/Wait
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "milliseconds": 2000
}

### 8. 截取当前页面截图（全屏）
GET {{BrowserAPI_HostAddress}}/api/Browser/Screenshot?fullPage=true
Accept: application/json

### 9. 截取当前页面截图（仅视口）
GET {{BrowserAPI_HostAddress}}/api/Browser/Screenshot?fullPage=false
Accept: application/json

### 10. 获取当前页面 URL
GET {{BrowserAPI_HostAddress}}/api/Browser/CurrentUrl
Accept: application/json

### 11. 获取当前页面标题
GET {{BrowserAPI_HostAddress}}/api/Browser/Title
Accept: application/json

### 12. 点击搜索结果中的第一个链接（示例，需根据实际 Arian 快照调整 role/name）
POST {{BrowserAPI_HostAddress}}/api/Browser/Click
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "role": "link",
  "name": "Browser Automation",
  "timeoutMs": 8000
}

### 13. 关闭浏览器并清理资源
POST {{BrowserAPI_HostAddress}}/api/Browser/Close
Accept: application/json

### 14. Ai交流
POST {{BrowserAPI_HostAddress}}/api/chat/send
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "你好",
  "stream": false
}